txt.en: 'To think it would be easy. You must venture these paths to secure my freedom.'
'You have done it! I shall soon be free!'
'I did not lie to you. You have set me free.'
'The maiden you seek is no longer. I suggest you leave.'
'Any attempt to save me and cleanse this body will be for naught. You have been warned!'
'Your maiden is dead. See her remains for yourself!'
'I devoured her, and I shall devour you as well!'
'I grow ever weak from my shackles.'
You must have completed 'Discovery: Eithel Gwaur, the Filth-well' to play this instance.
'Its defeat is the only path to my chamber. You must hurry!'
'There are more trials towards my freedom. Quickly now.'
